value: SE Colombia to s Venezuela, e Peru and w-c Amazonian Brazil

Southern Venezuela in the region about Mt. Duida, the upper Caura and the upper Paragua; Colombia in Intendencia de Vaupes (Macacuni) and Comisaria de Caqueta (Morelia); eastern Peru in Department of Loreto; 2 Brazil on the upper Rio Negro, the Rio Cauaburi and the Rio Madeira.
